title: Let's Watch TV: Stuck
description:
This week, Fran and Joe watch a strange show from TLC called Stuck. Mama Fran shares stories from her time working in the ER and Joe is reminded of kindergarteners fondness for sticking beads in bodily orifices before another Wild Story Wednesday.
